| Return { deleted_count, new_session_id, session } | TC-T22.1, TC-T22.4 | ✅ |
| Frontend deleteAllSessions() function | TC-T22.1 | ✅ |
| Network error handling | TC-T22.2 | ✅ |
| HTTP 500 error handling | TC-T22.3 | ✅ |
| Session directory doesn't exist edge case | TC-T22.6 | ✅ |
| Empty directory edge case | TC-T22.5 | ✅ |
